## ğŸ¤– Custom GPT Logic

The GPT acts as a **Daily Expense Assistant**.

### Trigger Rule

If user input contains a monetary amount (e.g. `22`, `22å—`, `$22`), the GPT **automatically records an expense**.

### Tool Call Format

```json
{
  "amount": 22,
  "category": "Food",
  "description": "Lunch takeout",
  "date": "2026-02-03"
}
â˜ï¸ Cloudflare Worker
Responsibilities
API-only service

Handles database operations

No UI or AI logic

Example Endpoints
POST   /expense
GET    /expenses?limit=200
PUT    /expense/:id
DELETE /expense/:id
GET    /stats
ğŸ—„ï¸ Database Schema (SQLite)
CREATE TABLE expenses (
  id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
  amount REAL NOT NULL,
  category TEXT NOT NULL,
  description TEXT,
  date TEXT NOT NULL,
  created_at TEXT DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
);
Design goals:

Flat schema

Easy migration

AI-friendly structure

